These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros, prince, chaman, alhambra, swisher, tiparillo
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere between the swisher-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##7
 3. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the swisher-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##7
 4. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the swisher-smoker##8
 6. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 8. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##7
 9. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the chaman-smoker##8
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Cigar   | alhambra | ritmeester | oliveros | prince | chaman | swisher | tiparillo |

