.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  teacher, writer, software-developer, designer, doctor, musician, entrepreneur
 1. the musician is the musician##1
 2. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5
 3. the musician is somewhere to the right of the writer##5
 4. the writer is in an even position##4
 5. the musician is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
 6. the designer is somewhere to the left of the writer##5
 7. the teacher is on the left of the doctor##1
 8. the musician is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 9. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
10. the doctor is not to the left of the teacher##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Job   | designer | writer | musician | entrepreneur | software-developer | teacher | doctor |

