.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: light-blue, turquise, black, blue, ebony, blood-red, emerald
 1. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
 2. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 5. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 6. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the person who likes light-blue##8
 7. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes turquise##7
 8. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes light-blue is not to the right of the person who likes black##8
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Color   | ebony | blood-red | blue | emerald | light-blue | black | turquise |

