.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, techno, electronic, disco, jazz, country, funk
 1. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the fan of techno##7
 2. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
 3. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of country##1
 4. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the fan of funk and the fan of techno##7
 5. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the fan of disco##7
 6. the fan of disco is somewhere between the fan of folk and the fan of funk##7
 7. the fan of folk is not to the right of the fan of country##8
 8. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 9. the fan of funk is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | folk | disco | funk | jazz | techno | country |

