 6. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
 7. the person eating lemon is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person eating cranberry##7
 8. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person eating cranberry and the person eating cauliflower##2
