 5. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 6. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
 7. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 8. the art-deco house is not to the left of the modern house##8
 9. the art-deco house is somewhere between the cottage house and the victorian house##7
10. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
11. the modern house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
12. the cape-cod house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |     7      |
